wiki.content: “Two®” marks Lil Uzi Vert’s first song of his album Luv Is Rage 2, and is named specifically to show Uzi’s transition from his 2015 album Luv Is Rage. On the track he discusses the fact that he now has money and power in the music industry. The song explains how “SoundCloud rappers” are biting his style and stealing his cadence to attempt to ride the wave for fame. The song also talks about how people should be thanking him for innovating the hip-hop industry because he feels like a lot of people wouldn’t be popping right now if it wasn’t for him and his crazy style.
